scheduled_maintenances.name: [Global][Hosted Private Cloud] - VMware vCenter Server maintenance notification

incident_updates.body: As part of our continuous improvement plan, maintenance is scheduled on our Hosted Private Cloud offer. Start time : 12/11/2024 08:00 UTC End time : 15/11/2024 16:00 UTC Service impact : Management will be temporarily unavailable for 1h30 during the maintenance. And all hosts will be put in maintenance mode. Service improvement : As part of our continuous improvement policy, we are rolling out an upgrade for hosts and vCenter Server services. An individual communication will be sent before the upgrade begins. Thank you for your understanding.
